<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My Hometown</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* AliceBlue background */
            color: #333333; /* Dark gray text color */
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #000080; /* Navy blue heading color */
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .hometown-img {
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            width: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #000080;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to My Hometown!</h1>
    <!-- Replace "path_to_your_image.jpg" with your image path/URL -->
    <img src="path_to_your_image.jpg" alt="Description of hometown" class="hometown-img">
    <p>
        This is a simple web page about my lovely hometown. We have beautiful scenery, a rich history, and friendly people.
        The internal CSS is used to style this page with an attractive background, text colors, and font.
    </p>
    <p>
        Hope you enjoy the simple design!
    </p>
</body>
</html>